{"tid":104851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實連台灣人都話國語係北京胡語！！！","createTime":"2017-02-02T12:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T08:21:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aff993e53abdd5269b1f271fcd45222ae6d846e9","tid":104851,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:08:53.000Z","msg":"其實連台灣人都話國語係北京胡語！！！<br />\n<a href=\"http://taiwanwe.org/discuss01.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaiwanwe.org%2Fdiscuss01.htm&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=31c46c3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://taiwanwe.org/discuss01.htm</a> <br />\n漢人未來台灣之前，整個台灣平地都是平埔族的天下，在漢人入侵的強勢文化與統治下，平埔族的語言、文化、人種全部消失無蹤。北京語（<span style=\"color: red;\">國語，應該稱為北京胡語較適合</span>）並非純漢語，在五胡亂華及元宋，胡族入侵的強大政治力量下，原來北方官話的漢語與胡語混合，形成入聲消失，簡化成四聲的變種語言──北京胡語。政治、教育及傳播媒體消滅台語的力量，在國民黨的掌控下，實在太恐怖了，台灣各族群的語言與文化，在國民黨外來政權的殖民地心態統治下，如不大力挽救，必然走上平埔族滅亡的命運。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話國語唔係普通話唔係胡語嘅人仲有咩解釋？！"},{"pid":"151d152c61d6624b80750f116a56c59fedc52682","tid":104851,"uid":7355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"應該講返福建話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1398c4884719752a557bcd6359e59e94e5e21c90","tid":104851,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:44:23.000Z","msg":"國民黨推普勁過共產黨"},{"pid":"f04253f047208334472ac68e6196182db3fb1e29","tid":104851,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"胡語同粵語都唔係純正漢語"},{"pid":"d04c4a47a73e933565c3bd2adf98451fcf76f181","tid":104851,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胡語同粵語都唔係純正漢語</blockquote><br />\n冇一個語言叫「純正漢語」<br />\n南蠻粵語同滿州胡語就更加"},{"pid":"24b2999bf2a4600124a1253bf9224d5405020dcd","tid":104851,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國民黨推普勁過共產黨</blockquote><br />\n一隻手掌拍唔響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都要台灣人幫手"},{"pid":"2597467424d2ebf22c5bc8564b3bc0e6addde2ea","tid":104851,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24b2999bf2a4600124a1253bf9224d5405020dcd","tid":104851,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國民黨推普勁過共產黨</blockquote><br />\n一隻手掌拍唔響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都要台灣人幫手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"有冇睇歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果時超高壓統治,學校禁台語,<br />\n電視台版政府控制,台語仲俾人攞黎恥笑,<br />\n已經去到唔講國語生存唔到既地步,<br />\n其實支共都想強行用普通話消滅其他語言,<br />\n廣州已經搞緊,香港因為全世界睇住,<br />\n所以只能慢慢黎,搞下普教中,新移民淡化,<br />\n唔可以渣支槍迫你唔準講"},{"pid":"16dacd50d97e73560b975782035fd69d7bc91564","tid":104851,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"推返上來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}